Q) runnable interface\par
class MyRunnable implements Runnable \{\par
    public void run() \{\par
        for (int i = 1; i <= 5; i++) \{\par
            System.out.println(Thread.currentThread().getName() + " is running : " + i);\par
        try \{\par
            Thread.sleep(1000);  // Sleep after the loop\par
